The role of muscle depletion and visceral adiposity in HCC patients aged 65 and 
over undergoing TACE.

Lim J(1), Kim KW(2), Ko Y(3), Jang IY(4), Lee YS(1)(5), Chung YH(1)(5), Lee 
HC(1)(5), Lim YS(1)(5), Kim KM(1)(5), Shim JH(1)(5), Choi J(1)(5), Lee D(6)(7).

