"We improved our life because I cut my drinking": Qualitative analysis of a 
brief intervention for people with alcohol use disorder in Ethiopian primary 
health care.

Zewdu S(1), Hanlon C(2), Fekadu A(3), Medhin G(4), Teferra S(5).

