Efficacy and safety of givosiran for acute hepatic porphyria: 24-month interim 
analysis of the randomized phase 3 ENVISION study.

Ventura P(1), Bonkovsky HL(2), Gouya L(3), Aguilera-Peiró P(4), Montgomery 
