Sulfated exopolysaccharides from Porphyridium cruentum: A useful strategy to 
extend the shelf life of minced beef meat.

Ben Hlima H(1), Smaoui S(2), Barkallah M(1), Elhadef K(2), Tounsi L(1), Michaud 
P(3), Fendri I(4), Abdelkafi S(5).

